b"a giant green/mossy  titan emerged out of no where and enslaved the whole humanity. it forced us to rebuilt earth, and had us taking care of plants and trees all over the world. in matter of few years the whole planet turned green like u see in apocalypse-themed movies where towns turned into jungles, due to lack of human activity. few years later i found a way to sneak away from monsters sigh and i discovered a portal-like thingy. apparently, the mossy titan trapped us in an alternate reality, and pass through the portal is our real world.
i rallied up humanity ( whitch for some reason , the whole population it was ~20 ppl ) and made out a plan to escape the fake earth-
as we were about to escape , the titan burst into tears. apperently, the titan was earth's spirit, full of mother instict. humans ruining plants and trees, made mother earth, having no kids to take care off, so it felt empty. 

1 would say, the mother earth enslaved humanity to restore flora on earth- her kids, but noooooooo, the mother earth enslaved humanity, and treated humanity as her kids. yep. she gave 0 shit about plants, she just wanted to be a mother figure towards something. she forced us to re-build flora on earth, just to distract us from the truth.

as the truth was revealed, humanity pittied mother earth, and we promised to help rebuild flora on real earth, so mother earth has something to be a mother figure towards."
